docs.lead_paragraph: OFFAL AGREEMENT.-- An arrangement has been effected with the Jersey City Common Council Committee on Health, by ANTHONY SAUER , for the removal of dead horses and other dead animals, blood, offal bones and other refuse matter and other nuisances from the City, without cost to him and without expense to the city.

headline.main: THE QUARANTINE WAR.; Arrests at Old quarantine. THE MILITARY INVOKED. Latest from Seguine's Point. ONE OF THE INCENDIARIES WOUNDED. Particulars of teh Approach and Attacj.

docs.lead_paragraph: Captain WALLING and Mr. JOSEPH QUICK, Jr., one of the policemen, came up from Seguine's Point on Monday. Captain WALLING, on Saturday, went over to Keyport for provisions, and upon his return, about dusk, be observed two rockets sent up-one from Eeltown, and the other from near the Great Kills.

headline.main: LATER FROM HAVANA.; Arrival of the Empire City--The Spanish Fleet Preparing for Sea-Yellow Fever Moderate--General News.

docs.lead_paragraph: The Empire City, Captain JNo. McGOWAN, left New-Orleans on the 5th inst. and Havana on the 9th At Havana there is nothing specially new. The Spanish fleet is reported preparing for sea, " destination unknown." There is very little yellow fever prevalent for the season, and not of an epidemic type. The prices of sugar and molasses remain unchanged since last advices.

docs.lead_paragraph: The Steamship Star of the West, With news from California to June 20, and bringing later advices from South and Central America, the West Coast of Mexico, the Sandwich Islands, Oregon, arrived about 1 o'clock this morning. The news From California is generally unimportant, the principal excitement being political, incident upon the changes--progressing and prospective--going on in the Federal offices. The Star of the West brings $1,521,676. A great stagnation is reported in the markets.

docs.lead_paragraph: The long-threatened, much-talked-of, and finallyscouted rumor of a contemplated attack upon the new Quarantine station at Sequine's Point by the disaffected property-bolder and indignant oyster-vender of that region has finally come off, and all further doubt--if doubts exist-as to the intentions of the insurgents may now be dismissed;
